# HCP Terraform Changelog

## 2026

### April 2026

#### IP Allowlists for HCP Terraform
**Released:** April 1, 2026

Organization owners can now create IP allowlists that govern user and agent access to their organizations.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/users-teams-organizations/ip-allowlists)

---

### March 2026

#### AWS Dynamic Credentials Quick Setup using AWS Temporary Delegation
**Released:** March 31, 2026

HCP Terraform can automatically set up dynamic credentials for AWS using AWS temporary permission delegation.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/dynamic-provider-credentials/aws-configuration/quick-setup)


#### Registry Artifact Tagging
**Released:** March 31, 2026

Enables tagging and categorization of modules and providers in the private registry for better organization, discovery, and lifecycle management.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/registry/manage/tags)


#### HCP Terraform Optional Control of Org Membership (SSO Linked Accounts)
**Released:** March 31, 2026

New security control requiring organization members to link their HCP SSO accounts, ensuring consistent identity management and access control.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/users-teams-organizations/single-sign-on)


#### Maximum Time-to-Live (TTL) for API Tokens
**Released:** March 26, 2026

The max TTL introduces guardrails around API token lifetimes. This helps eliminate long-lived tokens and enables stronger, more consistent security practices across your organization.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/users-teams-organizations/single-sign-on)


#### Workspaces UI update
**Released:** March 11, 2026

Updates are made to the filtering experience, allowing for faster and easier ways to apply and remove different combinations of filters while also knowing exactly what filters are applied to the table view.



#### Terraform Billing Run Insights
**Released:** March 9, 2026

Enhanced billing and cost tracking features providing detailed insights into Terraform run costs, resource usage, and infrastructure spend patterns.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/cost-estimation)

---

### February 2026

#### Speculative Plan Autoscaling
**Released:** February 3, 2026

Update to the HCP Terraform Operator that allows Kubernetes to intelligently scale agent pods based on pending PR-driven plans.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/agents/agents)

#### Project-scoped Remote State Sharing
**Released:** February 2, 2026

This feature allows users to share remote state across all workspaces in a project, in addition to existing global and specific workspace options

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/workspaces/settings#remote-state-sharing)

---

### January 2026

#### HCP Terraform - Improve Performance / Processing Time of Policies
**Released:** January 28, 2026

Performance optimizations reducing policy evaluation time, enabling faster plan and apply operations while maintaining security and compliance checks.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/policy-enforcement)
