## 2025

### December 2025

#### PCI DSS Policies (AWS)
**Released:** December 1, 2025

Ready-to-use Sentinel policy sets designed to automatically verify AWS infrastructure against PCI DSS compliance standards.

[Documentation](https://github.com/hashicorp/policy-library-pcidss-policy-set-for-aws-terraform)

---

### October 2025

#### Python SDK (python-tfe)
**Released:** October 28, 2025

The first official, HashiCorp-supported Python client for HCP Terraform, featuring Pydantic-based type safety and broad API coverage.

[Documentation](https://github.com/hashicorp/python-tfe)

#### Terraform MCP Server
**Released:** October 23, 2025

Added support for Terraform Search and Actions, allowing AI agents to discover resources and trigger Day 2 workflows.

[Documentation](https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-mcp-server)

#### Terraform Search
**Released:** October 20, 2025

Global resource visibility across all workspaces and organizations, allowing teams to find and audit any managed cloud resource.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/language/import?product_intent=terraform)

#### Terraform Actions
**Released:** October 20, 2025

A framework for defining and running "Day 2" task-based operations (like snapshots or health checks) outside the standard apply lifecycle.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/language/invoke-actions)

#### HCP Terraform EU Region
**Released:** October 1, 2025

The launch of a dedicated European control plane to support local data residency and GDPR compliance requirements.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/hcp/docs/hcp/regions)

---

### September 2025

#### NIST SP 800-53 Policies
**Released:** September 30, 2025

A new library of pre-written Sentinel policies to help organizations automate compliance with NIST 800-53 security controls.

[Documentation](https://registry.terraform.io/policies/hashicorp/nist-policy-set-for-aws-terraform/latest)

#### Stacks
**Released:** September 25, 2025

Enables managing multiple workspaces, providers, and environments as a single unit with a new orchestration engine.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/stacks)

#### Cloudability Run Task
**Released:** September 25, 2025

A new "Run Task" integration with IBM/Apptio Cloudability to provide proactive AWS cost governance during the plan phase.

[Documentation](https://www.ibm.com/docs/en/cloudability-commercial/cloudability-standard/saas?topic=governance-hcp-terraformterraform-enterprise)

#### Terraform MCP Server v0.3.0
**Released:** September 24, 2025

Version 0.3.0 released, adding support for workspace management, private registries, and triggering runs via AI agents.

[GitHub Releases](https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-mcp-server/releases)

#### ServiceNow Catalog
**Released:** September 4, 2025

Introduces native approval workflow support within the ServiceNow Service Catalog integration for HCP Terraform.

[Documentation](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cloud-docs/integrations/service-now)

